column5:
Introducing command.getType()

for AnnotationCommand, InsertNodeCommand,
and SwitchTextTypeCommand

Refactored data/Node

A schema is defined now via

MyNode.schema = {...}

Call initialize() for oo.extend'ed inline protos.

Component.extend({
  initialize: function() {
    // this gets called after construction
  }
});

OO.extend() and OO.inherit() support static properties.

- either defined using OO.extensible(clazz, staticProperties)
- or via proto.static = {...}
